@page "/profile/confuscious"

<h2>Meet Confuscious: Your New Best Friend</h2>
<div class="text-center mt-4">
    <!-- Large Image of the Dog -->
    <img src="https://www.boredpanda.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/644a230e3f5d4_l7ink8py2vta1__700.jpg"
         alt="Confuscious"
         class="img-fluid"
         style="width: 500px; height: 500px; object-fit: cover;">
</div>

<!-- Long Description Section -->
<div class="container mt-4">
    <p>
        Confuscious is a charming, intelligent, and spunky Dachshund looking for his forever home. With his short legs, long body, and
        playful personality, Confuscious is a classic example of why Dachshunds are one of the most beloved dog breeds in the world. Rescued
        from a tough situation, he has shown nothing but unconditional love and kindness toward everyone he meets.
    </p>
    <p>
        Dachshunds are known for their determination and adventurous spirit, and Confuscious is no exception. Whether it’s chasing a toy, exploring
        the neighborhood, or snuggling up on the couch for an afternoon nap, Confuscious loves spending time with his humans. His sweet, loyal nature makes
        him the perfect companion for both families and individuals looking for a cuddly and active four-legged friend.
    </p>
    <p>
        Confuscious would thrive in a home where he gets plenty of playtime, attention, and love. While he is great with children and other pets, his
        personality truly shines when he gets the care and routine he deserves. Dachshunds are known for their loyalty, and Confuscious will be a lifelong companion
        to the special family that opens their heart to him.
    </p>
    <p>
        If you think you can provide Confuscious with the loving forever home he deserves, don’t wait. Come meet this brave little adventurer and let
        him show you all the joy and companionship he can bring to your life. With his affectionate personality and charming smile, Confuscious is ready
        to be your new best friend!
    </p>
    <!-- Centered Button Section -->
    <div class="text-center mt-3">
        <form action="/submit" method="POST">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="window.location.href='/application-page'; return false;">Submit Application</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>

